- X' ≡ X·T (mod p)
- Y' ≡ Y·Z (mod p)
- Z' ≡ Z·T (mod p)
where p = 2^255 - 19
These formulas implement the conversion from completed ℙ¹ × ℙ¹ coordinates to projective
ℙ² coordinates.
-/

